==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ʌdʒəl|-ʌdʒəl]]

===Noun===
'''cudgel'''
# a short heavy stick used as a weapon
#: ''The guard hefted his [[cudgel]] menacingly at the inmates, the threat to swing glinted in his eye.''
====Translations====
*Finnish: [[nuija]], [[ryhmysauva]]

===Transitive verb===
'''to cudgel'''
# to strike someone with a cudgel
#: ''The officer was violently [[cudgel]]ed down in the midst of the rioters, with his own beatstick no less.''
